<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qlby mn kẖyrk mdywn lạ̹smk ạlgẖạly bḥlạwẗ ḥbk mftwn bygẖny̱ lyạly
 ḥbk bạlnʿmẗ mḍmwn msẖ bạlạ̉ʿmạl
 ạlqrạr - fy qlby sẖkr wtsbyḥ wḥmd mjyd
 lk yạ yswʿ ạlmsyḥ dạymạaⁿ byzyd
 2- ạ̹nt ạlly fdytny̱ wḥbytny wkstny bbrk wjʿltny mạlk wwạrtẖ llsmạʾ fy ạ̹bnk
 ṭwbạk yạ qlby ạ̹htf gẖny yswʿ byḥbk
 3- mbrwk kẖṭạyạnạ ạ̹tgẖfrt bdm yswʿ wlạ ʿạdt tạny tfṣlnạ ʿn ḥb yswʿ
 bạldm ạ̉nạ bạ̉htf wbạ̉gẖny̱ gẖạlb byswʿ</lyrics>
<title>fy qlby sẖkr wtsbyḥ</title>
</song>